{"tid":2032031,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"致香港人：我們都是這樣走過的","createTime":"2020-05-23T20:49:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T02:30:29.000Z","uid":317751,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1320bef37ca246ebbcd1c4ecf9777ff357d8f530","tid":2032031,"uid":317751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T20:49:06.000Z","msg":"回頭聽返 一首帶俾香港人共嗚既歌<br />\n香港人加油！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RGmWlU2EPF4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRGmWlU2EPF4&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=ca5623c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RGmWlU2EPF4</a>"},{"pid":"03aa164a4f807c377f454e5fedbfdf57e5e43c2b","tid":2032031,"uid":317751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T20:51:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b99f2a585eb87ec12daad2bef2e36c43966719a8","tid":2032031,"uid":80301,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T20:53:53.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"259c38972dbe3e9c4216c51830b567018853fdec","tid":2032031,"uid":204750,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T20:54:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"ea7547109f9762186b498fac44624866d4e6fac0","tid":2032031,"uid":317751,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T20:54:55.000Z","msg":"我們都是這樣走過的<br />\n原曲：我們都是這樣長大的<br />\n曲：徐沛昕<br />\n編：Wil/AC<br />\n詞/唱：雷霈晞<br />\n<br />\n人潮裏 誰都會錯或對<br />\n誰勇敢 誰拚命地沉睡<br />\n危難裏 人縱是極勞累<br />\n也都豁出去<br />\n<br />\n雲層裏 陽光散了又退<br />\n寒雨點 流到大地成淚<br />\n疑惑上帝怎能放任亦允許<br />\n害怕終失據<br />\n<br />\n*然而慶幸聯群結隊<br />\n揚言不怕沿途崎嶇<br />\n時而歡笑 時而怨懟<br />\n還會默然攜着面對<br />\n連儂見證 每次面臨鵝黃煙吹<br />\n撕抹不走的歷史 寫你我同一句<br />\n明明怯懦 明明畏懼<br />\n仍然堅信仍能急追<br />\n埋頭苦戰 從頭佔據<br />\n捱到盡頭<br />\n一起歸家去<br />\n<br />\n荼蘼開了<br />\n繁花內共同留守<br />\n抬頭能望飛絮*<br />\n<br />\n雲層裏 陽光散了又退<br />\n寒雨點 流到大地成淚<br />\n疑惑上帝怎能放任亦允許<br />\n害怕撐不下去<br />\n<br />\nRepeat *<br />\n<br />\n仍慶幸同途結聚<br />\n仍然深愛難離蝸居<br />\n曾同歡笑 曾同怨懟<br />\n期盼以後重拾堡壘<br />\n連儂刻過每個字也是燎火<br />\n撕抹不走的歷史 寫你我同一句<br />\n銀發亦徐徐結聚<br />\n情懷不老 情懷不衰<br />\n兒童青少成年晚歲<br />\n擁抱未來 不接受榨取<br />\n拼命去維護獅子山精髓<br />\n唯求無憾故此不撤就不退<br />\n<br />\n堪稱壯舉"},{"pid":"8dd6797f5837cdabb3a158ff6979736de65cbc1f","tid":2032031,"uid":317751,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T20:58:06.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e950631214ce568feeafed8676a0bd91646a93","tid":2032031,"uid":137706,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T21:02:41.000Z","msg":"香港人"},{"pid":"d5316b229c31380e2c0a0f1475910226e3fd25df","tid":2032031,"uid":194399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:24:41.000Z","msg":"成日都聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af39b489f18f9b6d5f5cb13b3e87bcedbf62b43","tid":2032031,"uid":56607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:29:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n0527<br />\n香港獨立 唯一出路<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LyckKqg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLyckKqg.gif&h=1dd408c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ebb92620cbc2247660d2be0c4dd36ddf2948b88","tid":2032031,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:30:26.000Z","msg":"幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075bcade6f27ab504fec7333edd4085ca352f75d","tid":2032031,"uid":296048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:30:29.000Z","msg":"thank you"}]}